# AWS S3 — file storage for uploads + AI-generated images.
# When AWS_S3_BUCKET (or the legacy AWS_BUCKETNAME) is set, file uploads
# go to S3 and tbl_files.url stores the public S3 URL. When unset, the
# backend falls back to local disk (only useful for dev).
